data.description: Very well kept brick house on 1.23 acre lot. This property is waiting for you and your family to call home. Home and driveway freshly pressure washed. All appliances and furniture convey (AS-IS at no value), unless you would like them removed. Includes 2 car detached garage building. Roof is around 5 years old, newer vinyl windows, HVAC 2 years old. Home has 11 closets total, 3 in master bedroom. Seller would prefer to sell this AS-IS for cash, or Owner Financing. Financing terms are minimum of 20k down, 5% simple interest(cheaper than most Banks currently), no-prepay penalty. Also No lender closing costs saves you around 3% $$$ upfront. You can pay off or refinance anytime in the future. You just need 20k down, and the fee's your attorney charges to close. No Credit Check Required! Must provide Proof of Funds for Cash offers or show proof down PMT for financing. Open house Saturday April 9th 12-3pm. Seller asking for offers by Monday APRIL 11TH at noon, and will make a decision and respond that evening by 8pm.
